Ontology Specification Draft

Abstract

The document explains the ontology for deepfake attacks. This is the first ontology in the deepfake domain and is developed using Web Ontology Language (OWL). The deepfake ontology provides a set of classes, properties, relations, and restrictions that can represent deepfake attacks in various contexts. The representation can help model essential information in a particular scenario like attack consequences and preventive measures. The first deepfake ontology can be enhanced by adding auxiliary entities and properties to model deepfake technology information for specialized applications.

This is a place holder text for the introduction. The introduction should briefly describe the ontology, its motivation, state of the art and goals.

Deepfake Attack Ontology : Description back to ToC

The Deepfake Attack Ontology describes essential information related to a deepfake attack scenario, such as deepfake creator, victim, manipulated multimedia, used algorithms, training data, attack motivation, consequences, preventive measures, and more.

SWRL rules

  • GovernmentInstitutesGetEffectedByConsequences
  • IndividualsGetEffectedByConsequences
  • PoliticiansCanAdoptPreventiveMeasures
  • PoliticiansGetEffectedByConsequences
  • PublicFiguresCanAdoptPreventiveMeasures

GovernmentInstitutesGetEffectedByConsequencesback to ToC or SWRL ToC



Government Institute c(?) -> Is Effected By op(?,?GlobalConflict) , Is Effected By op(?,?Infocalypse) , Is Effected By op(?,?NationalSecurityConcerns)

IndividualsGetEffectedByConsequencesback to ToC or SWRL ToC



Individual c(?) -> Is Effected By op(?,?IndividualPrivacyBreach) , Is Effected By op(?,?IndividualSecurityConcern) , Is Effected By op(?,?PublicDefamation)

PoliticiansCanAdoptPreventiveMeasuresback to ToC or SWRL ToC



Politician c(?) -> can Adopt Preventive Measure op(?,?ScrutinizeMediaContent) , can Adopt Preventive Measure op(?,?RaisePublicAwareness) , can Adopt Preventive Measure op(?,?BuildAndReformDigitalPrivacyAndSecurityRules) , can Adopt Preventive Measure op(?,?OfferIncentivesToPublicOnDigitalLiteracy)

PoliticiansGetEffectedByConsequencesback to ToC or SWRL ToC



Politician c(?) -> Is Effected By op(?,?GlobalConflict) , Is Effected By op(?,?NationalSecurityConcerns)

PublicFiguresCanAdoptPreventiveMeasuresback to ToC or SWRL ToC



Public Figure c(?) -> can Adopt Preventive Measure op(?,?SocialMediaAccountAccessSecurity) , can Adopt Preventive Measure op(?,?RaisePublicAwareness) , can Adopt Preventive Measure op(?,?AntiPhishingTechnqiues)

Legend back to ToC

c: Classes
op: Object Properties
dp: Data Properties
ni: Named Individuals
